# Frontend Standards

## Source Of Truth

The codebase is the frontend source of truth. Figma is historical only and is not a design platform, approval gate, or read-only constraint.

## Brand And UX

- Use Montserrat and MyMoolah brand green `#86BE41`; use blue `#2D8CCA` as secondary.
- Mobile wallet is mobile-first; portal is desktop-first.
- Prefer existing components, overlays, CSS variables, and design-system tokens.
- Keep UI accessible: labels, focus states, keyboard support, contrast, and screen-reader text.

## Wallet Navigation

For new wallet overlays/pages, verify:
- `TopBanner` inclusion where appropriate.
- Scrollable body and sticky `BottomNavigation`.
- Relevant route allowlists in `App.tsx` and `BottomNavigation.tsx`.

## Duplicate Files

Some wallet pages have `pages/` and `components/` copies. If you touch one, search for the duplicate and keep routed behavior consistent.
